{"title":"信","authors":["李泛"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":11,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李泛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从远方的家乡寄来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是十二岁小弟弟写的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×     ×          ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二哥："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你来信说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在部队里身体很好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱全家都很高兴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里大家都好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸、妈妈、大哥、嫂嫂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天去地里生产；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和妹妹天天去上学。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈告诉我："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你去参军那一年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才七岁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里还没闹翻身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷得没吃没穿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在有了好光景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——能够读书。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要好好用功"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才对得起二哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才对得起解放军、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听了妈妈的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读书挺用功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年、今年都得“第一”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在我已学会了写信。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一个好消息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年年成真好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱家夏收麦子五石四，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋收小米高粱六石五，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷子二石八，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有大箩大箩的玉米、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山药蛋……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种了十三亩棉花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次就摘了九百斤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花又白，朵又大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱全家都乐坏啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们把多余的粮食"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换来一条大黄牯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又打了一辆新车。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要再给大家做件新棉褂！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱村家家光景都差不多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——不愁吃、不愁穿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是眼看好日子到啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可恨美国鬼子又来侵略！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"区政府号召大家："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“反对美国挑拨战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫世界和平！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱村连娃儿都签了名！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天村长又报告说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国鬼子在咱们东北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丢了炸弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又扫机关枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人听了又气又恨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家要用实际行动反对侵略。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱家决定今年要加缴公粮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二百斤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里有他，有大哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切不用你记挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只希望你保重身体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心一意保卫国家！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"………………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×          ×            ×"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是歌唱新生活的诗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是反对美国强盗的抗议书！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它留给我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最幸福的感情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最勇敢的战斗意志！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的小弟弟、父亲……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一定不会忘记！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一定不会忘记！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五○、十、二十五日于青岛"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}